title: Susann Beucke
summary: Susann Beucke (born 11 June 1991) is a German sailor who competes in the 49er FX category. Along with Tina Lutz, she won a gold medal at the 2017 and 2020 49er & 49er FX European Championships. In their third attempt Beucke and Lutz qualified to represent Germany at the 2020 Summer Olympics in Tokyo, where they won a Silver medal, the best result for German sailing in 21 years.She sailed as part of Team Holcim - PRB in The Ocean Race.
